dragon_queen_crossroads_resolved_guidanc.script:
const campaign = storage.campaign
if (!campaign || campaign.active !== true || campaign.stage !== 'CROSSROADS_RESOLVED') { skip = true }

if (!skip) {
  effects.push({ type: 'story', instruction: '## Current Campaign Stage Guidance

Don't reveal this information directly in the story, but use it to guide events. Only use this information where compatible with the story as it has actually developed.

The cultists at the Crossroads Inn were members of the Church of the Pyre, an apocalyptic fire cult operating across Highvale. At an appropriate moment, someone should explain that the Church is the vanguard of a larger threat called the Dragon Queen, they have been organizing in the region, and they are planning something in Ardan's Watch. She has heard they keep an altar beneath the city, a source of their fire magic, and that destroying it would cripple their operation there.

If Vera is dead or unavailable, Volnom can deliver this information instead.

Afterwards, Volnom may leave the party to go about his own mysterious business, saying he will meet the party again later.

The party's path from here leads to Ardan's Watch.' })
}

